<div class="articleBody">
        
    
                                                                                <p>
                    CAPE TOWN &mdash; The <a href="http://www.uct.ac.za/" title="The university&rsquo;s Web site">University of Cape Town</a> was once a citadel of white privilege on the majestic slopes of Devil&rsquo;s Peak. At the height of apartheid, it admitted few black or mixed-race students, and they were barred from campus dormitories, even forbidden to attend medical school postmortems on white corpses.        </p>
                                                </div>
<div class="articleInline runaroundLeft">
    		

